name: Marid Pavilion
category: Decorative
footprint: 3x3
facing: no
shadow: yes
blocks_light: yes
height: 2.5
placement: center
room_types: elemental-water-node, aquatic-shrine, sunken-temple, merfolk-grotto
typical_count: single
clusters_with: pearl-obelisk, pearl-cluster, water-node-core, coral-pillar
notes: Ornate underwater pavilion with domed center; single centerpiece per chamber
