# Platform inner ring
poly 1.50,0.40 2.05,0.60 2.30,1.25 2.30,1.75 2.05,2.40 1.50,2.60 0.95,2.40 0.70,1.75 0.70,1.25 0.95,0.60 fill #a0d8e8 0.70
